    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a M-Variable Lock differential for optimal corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-strung valvetrain and bottom end are sorted. While the exterior shows minor signs of use consistent with its driver-focused history, the mechanical integrity and drivetrain response are exceptional.",
