    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained car that is ready for the road. The exterior is finished in a timeless coat that still holds a high-quality shine, though I have noted a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch from standard use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the upholstery is in great shape, showing only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s seat. Every feature, from the heated seats to the intuitive infotainment system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. It has been serviced regularly, with the most recent oil change and multi-point inspection completed just 500 miles ago. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and confident. This is a complete, honest car that delivers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' depreciation. Documentation of the service history is available for your review.",
